data.description: 4 level home in the heart of Vista Grande Terrace!  The two door garage walks into the property on the lower level which features a half bath, laundry area and the large family room with a fireplace.  The front walk way takes you up to the main floor where the front entrances opens into a large living room with windows to let in all the natural light, a formal dining area sits between the living room and kitchen.  The kitchen has ample storage as well as an eating nook and walks out to the back yard patio.  Upstairs are 2 secondary bedrooms and a full hall bath as well as the primary bedroom with an attached 3/4 bath. The lower fourth level is bonus space with three rooms and a closet.
